  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A very short <u>RPG</u> with action battles. The first entry of Clarent Saga.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > action RPG battles inspired by the 16-bit Action JRPG; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > soundtrack composed by Hiroki Kikuta and reminiscent of the 16-bit Action JRPG; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > pixel graphics reminiscent of 16-bit JRPG; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 difficulties.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the evil cult of Brax summons its demon lord, can raider Alex use the Clarent sword to stop them from taking over and enslaving everyone? A simple and short RPG,</p>",
